reviewText: Okay, this is one of those anime's that is hard not love (or laugh at, for  that matter).  Normally I don't really like subtitled anime's, unless it's  Sailor Moon, but this was completly different!  The video just kept  cracking me up, until I was in tears with laughter!  The main characters  are Malon, Akiro(sp?), Roll, Short, and Monbran.  If you like comedies like  Tenchi Muyo, Ranma 1/2, then this video is for you.  Check it out!
